steps.name: Click on chevron and select 'Move' in dropdown menu for 'FolderChild' project
Select parent folder 'FolderParent' in dropdown and click 'Move'
Get the list of breadcrumbs items as text
Expected Result: The folder 'FolderChild' is successfully moved from 'My views' page to the parent folder 'FolderParent' using the dropdown menu, and the breadcrumbs are updated accordingly.
